item.title: Track dump (Auxy)
item.dc:creator: ThoughtfulNoise
item.description:
I’d pull ‘Fine By Me’ (both versions) as, to my ears, they have all the right parts to be finished as a great track.

The mix and sound choices/design would benefit from more attention. That great lead melody in the latter half is being a little overwhelmed by the brightness of the synth chords, so maybe something to look at there.

Haven’t even checked out the others yet, but wanted to say that Fine By Me has a solid foundation that warrants more attention.
